    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car shows its age with some visible wear on the interior upholstery and a few minor scuffs and dings on the exterior. It has been regularly serviced, but prospective buyers should expect the typical maintenance needs associated with a vehicle of this age and mileage. It's a solid, functional car that gets the job done without the premium price of a showroom model.",
