    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero imperfections, scratches, or dents. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather upholstery that remains supple and shows no signs of wear, and all electronic features function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in peak performance, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history, ensuring a smooth and powerful driving experience that feels brand new.",
